    $( A natural number is even iff its square is even. $)
    nnesq $p |- ( ( A / 2 ) e. NN <-> ( ( A ^ 2 ) / 2 ) e. NN ) $=
      ( c2 cdiv co cn wcel cexp cmulc nnmulclt anidms 2nn mpan 2re recn nncn
